You see this behavior because you had used an absolute number against `top` property against the classes `.team-card .card-body`; what we could do is assign the following: `top:calc(100% - 89px);` which is the complete height of the `card-body` and we remove 89px which is the height for the `card-title` and `card-text`...

Working **snippet** below:

&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: true babel: false --&gt;

